{
  "message": "feat(fuzz): extend einsum_subscripts corpus with 16 edge-case seeds\n\nNew seeds covering:\n- Empty subscript string\n- 3D/4D contractions and permutations\n- Multi-operand cases (4-5 operands)\n- Long chain contractions\n- Double trace operations\n- Cycle contractions\n- Malformed ellipsis patterns\n- Implicit-only notation\n- Scalar-to-matrix broadcasting\n\nBrings corpus from 18 to 34 seeds.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
